	measure 'QK Target Fulfilment' = ```
			
			    VAR _targetbase = [Target QK]
			    VAR _firstinterval = IF(round([Ø QK], 2) < _targetbase + 0.2001, 1, 0)
			    VAR _secondinterval = IF(AND(round([Ø QK], 2) >= _targetbase + 0.2001, round([Ø QK], 2) < _targetbase + 0.4001), 1, 0)
			
			    RETURN 
			        IF(_firstinterval = 1, 0, IF(_secondinterval = 1, 1, 2))
			    // VAR _targetbase = [Target Note]
			    // VAR _firstinterval = IF(round([Ø Note], 2) <= _targetbase + 0.2001, 1, 0)
			    // VAR _secondinterval = IF(round([Ø Note], 2) <= _targetbase + 0.3001, 1, 0)
			
			    // RETURN 
			    //     IF(_firstinterval = 1, 0, IF(_secondinterval = 1, 1, 2))
			```
		formatString: 0
		displayFolder: 3 Targets
		lineageTag: 011c5c91-0e5e-4561-acb1-cb6bf7716f59

