	measure 'B,B1 Target Fulfilment' = ```
			
			    VAR _target = [Target Ø B]
			    VAR _firstinterval = IF(ROUND([Ø B,B1], 2) < _target + 0.4001, 1, 0)
			    VAR _secondinterval = IF(AND(ROUND([Ø B,B1], 2) >= _target + 0.4001, ROUND([Ø B,B1], 2) < _target + 0.9001), 1, 0)
			
			    RETURN 
			    IF(_firstinterval = 1, 0, IF(_secondinterval = 1, 1, 2))
			```
